HEADWORD: Roborate
<hw>Rob"o*rate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>roboratus</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>roborare</ets> to strengthen, fr.
<ets>robur</ets>, <ets>roboris</ets>, strength.]</ety> <def>To give
